Brix was walking back behind the bounty hunters, guns still aimed at 
them. Inside Octociz and Brix were talking.

Good job, Brix.

Don't thank me. Thank Bronco. I'm just glad I held onto my loyalty, 
or he would've killed everyone.

Well, why you were fighting, I was running scans for pods. One just 
recently crashed in North Dakota. It still has the ability to give 
robotic forms. After we lock these three up, we have to go there.

All right. Finaly see what you look like.

Brix/Octociz still looked ahead, watching the hunters for any sort of 
move.
